Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on Class of '09...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 我们会彼此握手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out here, we shake each other's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（现在）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 我不是来买牛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm not here to buy a cow, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-值得吗  -他们自己暴露了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was it worth it? They revealed themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他们计画攻击的目标是什么  -我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are they planning to attack? Us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以看清楚 你听到消息时脸上的表情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get to see the expression on your face when you hear the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些逮捕行动理由不明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are inexplicable arrests.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（未来）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你知 我知 -不 参议员 我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know it, I know it. No, Senator, I don't know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波伊特探员 你一直被蒙蔽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Special Agent Poet, you've been lied to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个系统会自己建立连结\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This system is making connections on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:01:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是跟我们截然不同的智慧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is an intelligence nothing like our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}联邦凶杀案\N第一季第四集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（过去 1996年）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嫌犯要进入公寓了 -收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Suspect is entering the apartment. Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌犯自己一个人 没看到他的女友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Suspect is alone. No sign of his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 准备进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Copy. Moving in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-联调局 开门 -开门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}FBI. Open up. Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手举起来 趴下 快点 趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hands up! Get down! Gun! Stay on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该待在车内\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should stay in the van.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去抓他 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get off me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 放开我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get him, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联调局 不要动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}FBI! Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 茱儿…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit. Drew. Drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她应该要待在车内的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was supposed to stay in the van.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她为什么会在这里  她到底在这里做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why was she there? What the hell was she doing? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撑着点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我当探员的第一把手枪 西格绍尔P228\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was my weapon as an agent. A SIG Sauer p228.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你开过枪吗 长官  我是说在出任务时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you ever fire it, ma'am? On duty, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我从未开过枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查局第一把制式武器 是四吋枪管的柯特警用左轮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Bureau's first official weapon. A four-inch barreled Colt Police revolver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在1934年发给毕业班学员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Issued to the class of 1934 at graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在使用的主要武器是克拉克23\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Today the primary weapon we use is the Glock 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把叫做红把手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one is called the red handle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为枪管塞住 撞针也移除了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because the barrel has been blocked and the firing pin removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练期间 你们在基地要带着这把枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}During your training, you will carry these around the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是要你们熟悉它的重量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want you to get accustomed to the weight of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触感 以及概念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The feel of them. The idea of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长官 概念是指什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The idea of them, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取人性命意谓着什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What it means to take a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒着自己的生命危险意谓着什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What it means to risk your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非想要开枪 否则探员不会拔枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A special agent doesn't draw their gun unless they intend to fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你觉得自己无法取人性命 那你就当不成探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you decide that you cannot take a life, you cannot be a special agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你拿到武器 请跟班上同学说一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you receive your weapon, I'd like you to tell the class
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己在枪枝方面的经验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about your own experiences with firearms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对枪很熟门熟路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know your way around a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成年之后就常跑靶场 长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I spent most of my adult life in a shooting range, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么样的靶场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the story of this range?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝加哥枪枝学院 长官 由一对和善的越南夫妇所经营\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chicago Gun Academy, sir. Ran by a lovely Vietnamese couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那里的人不是想要拿枪射谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The people going there weren't dreaming of shooting anybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们只是不想被人开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they just didn't want to be shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我第一次拿枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the first time I've ever held a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你何时提出申请的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When did you apply?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六个月前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们不接受 我说出来也没什么意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There wasn't any point in telling you if I wasn't going to be accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有告诉我们 是因为你知道我们会说不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't tell us because you knew we'd say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么现在要告诉我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why tell us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一阶段是测谎 如果我没有告诉你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The next stage is the polygraph. So if I hadn't told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那可能会出现在我的答案里 -乌尔 你在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}maybe it would show up in my answers. Hour. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你有麻省理工的学位 -他们喜欢我这点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a degree from MIT. They like that about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有其他人 会这样浪费自己的教育背景\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because nobody else would waste their education in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你一无所知的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is not a world you know anything about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们搭地铁上班 这样才不会在开车时被拦下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We take the Metro to work so we won't be stopped in our car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们度假时是搭车 这样才不会在机场被拦下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We take the car on vacation so we won't be stopped at the airports.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想要这样的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to live that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我想要有归属感 -这是你选择的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to feel part of something. And this is what you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他们需要我 爸 -但你为什么需要他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They want me, Dad. But why do you want them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会叫你做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What will they have you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-监视自己的同胞  -爸爸 这又不是秘密警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Spy on your own people? Baba, this isn't the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定会对我们家进行背景调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They must have carried out a background check on our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你把他们带进了我们的生活 -我们没什么好隐瞒的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've brought them into our lives. We have nothing to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是重点 那从来就不是重点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That doesn't matter. That has never mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生我们的气吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you angry with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是跟…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this about... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-其他事情有关吗  -那会是什么 妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something else? What might it be about, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a lonely child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你现在还是很孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps you're lonely still.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我会一直孤独下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I'll always be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要在这个国家有归属感有其他方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are other ways to feel a part of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要跟我们有不同感受也有其他方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And other ways to feel different from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们以我为荣 是不是太过奢求了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was it too much to hope that you'd be proud of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请抬起手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you lift your arms, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我可以自己来 -不行 得由我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I can do that. - No, it has to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把手摊平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you lay your hands flat, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解释一下你正在做什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could you explain what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有人问过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody ever asks that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椅子上有侦测动作的感测器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a sensor in the chair that detects movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是测量你呼吸频率的列线图管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These are pneumography tubes, measure your rate of respiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些会测量你的肤电活动 那个会量血压\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These measure electrodermal activity. That's for your blood pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测试大概要花两个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The test will take approximately two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你的答案没有反应 可能会花上四小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if your answers are unresponsive, it can take up to four.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的答案只能局限在是与否\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to limit your answers to yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你随时可以终止测试 但这样做会造成失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can stop the test at any time, but to do so would constitute a fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有权找律师 但这么做会…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you have the right to an attorney, but to call for one would...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Constitute a fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会紧张是正常的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's normal to be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不紧张 我是好奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not nervous. I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谁来解读这些反应  -我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who interprets the responses? I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你做过多少测试  -几百次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many tests have you done? Oh, hundreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年有五万人申请加入联邦调查局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are 50,000 applicants to the Bureau each year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府一定执行了几百万次这样的测试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The government must have carried out millions of these tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-经年累月 -你们会…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over the years. Do you... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜集资料吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}collect the data?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会以档案形式保存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We keep 'em on file.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是存放在集中式资料库吗  -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But is it on a centralized database? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些资料如果能交叉比对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't it make sense to cross-reference them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而非依赖单一个人的解读 不是更合理吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}rather than rely on one person's interpretation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是有李文和的案子 那个洛沙拉摩斯的核子科学家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was the case of Wen Ho Lee. Nuclear scientist at Los Alamos
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他被控当中国的间谍 -我知道这个案子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}accused of being a Chinese spy? I know the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他通过了能源部的测谎 但是当联调局重新检视同一份结果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He passed the DOE polygraph. But the FBI reexamined the same results
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们判定他在说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and they decided he was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把W88小型核弹头的秘密 泄漏给中国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That he had slipped China secrets about the miniaturized W88 warhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们把搜集到的资料 都放到集中式资料库\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe if you collated all the data on a central database,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许判读就不会那么主观了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it wouldn't be so subjective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 有些人不想要通过测试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, some people want to fail a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会故意采取某种方式 让自己退出流程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They deliberately flunk it in a way to drop out of the process 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又不会丢脸 如果你是这种情况 尽管说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without losing face. If that's you, just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以开始了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（现在 2023年）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾先前没有握手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me for not shaking your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一名海军陆战队员曾经跟我说… -抱歉 这名海军陆战队员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marine once told me... I'm sorry, this Marine, 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的朋友还是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is he a friend of yours, or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 好朋友 爱国者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Friend. Close friend. Patriot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说一个人在第一次杀人之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said after a man kills for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的皮肤味道会改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the smell of his skin changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你杀的第一个人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was she the first person you've killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把她从破烂的地方救出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I rescued her from squalor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修补她的牙齿 整理她的头发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I fixed her teeth, her hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顾她生存的一切所需\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Overlooked everything she had to do to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来你照顾过头了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, sounds like you overlooked quite a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你看不出来她恨你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because you couldn't see that she hated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的太太呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来我让你们两个人都成了凶手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like I made killers of you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为可以肯定地说 我们有正当理由 不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's safe to say that we had just cause, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“正当理由”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“正当理由”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑到我的牧场就是想要找这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that what you were looking for out at my ranch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“正当理由” 你一辈子都在找正当理由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Just cause." Yeah, you've been looking for that your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有了徽章和枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you got your badge and your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只需要“正当理由” 就可以为所欲为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All you needed was that "just cause" to get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为所欲为 是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"To get away with it," yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来谈谈“为所欲为”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's talk about that, "getting away with it."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为如果能为所欲为 我会去乱逛你的牧场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because getting away with it, I would've just strolled on your ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一枪打中你眉心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I would've shot you right between the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我应该这么做 因为如此一来你太太就不会丧命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And maybe I should've because then... your wife would still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的搭档不会躺在医院床上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My partner wouldn't be lying in a hospital bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太太也不会遭受攻击 但我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And my wife wouldn't have been attacked. But I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是蒙大拿阶级最高的联调局探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're the highest ranking FBI agent in Montana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是猎捕像我这样的人 你在例行的外勤工作当中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you doing on a routine piece of fieldwork
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if not hunting for folks like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 你已经梦想这天好几年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, you've been dreaming of that day for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们把事情说清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's... Let's be very clear about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能有很多身分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You may be many things, 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你绝对不是我的梦想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you are no dream of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们搞清楚了他们被逮时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have we figured out where they were driving to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-正要开车去哪里吗  -我们无法理解他们的路线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when they were caught? We can't make sense of their route.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（计算可能目的地）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有可能他们在声东击西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it possible that they were a diversion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了避开什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A diversion from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表现不错 乌尔 你是天生好手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice job, Hour. You're a natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰约 换你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tayo, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表现得很好…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射手准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shooter, stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好枪法 学员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice shooting, trainee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射手 准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shooter, stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么僵住了 学员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you freeze, trainee?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没有僵住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ma'am, I didn't freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不认为她是威胁 -为什么 她手拿武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't consider her to be a threat. Why not? She's armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她是谁呢 她是一名女性 看起来是专业人士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But who is she? She's a woman, she looks like a professional,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:15:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我猜她是执法人员 -她拿的不是克拉克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my guess would be law enforcement. She's not holding a Glock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯威森640 是下班警察可合法配戴的枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Smith & Wesson 640. Approved for off-duty police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你在那电光火石之间 判断她是下班的警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you decided in that split second she was an off-duty detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也用那些枪来保护自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, they also use those guns for personal protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可能是要逃离有暴力倾向的伙伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She could be escaping a violent partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这项测试不是要帮她写传记\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The test wasn't to write her biography.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们不用吗  如果我们要取她性命的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But don't we have to, if we're gonna take her life?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嘿 -嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚我很为你感到骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was proud of you back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were proud?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我说错话了 对吧  -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I said the wrong word, didn't I? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管正确的字眼是什么 那是我当时的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, whatever the, uh, the right word is, that is how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确的字眼不是你说了算吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't it up to you to decide what the right word is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你很难恭维 -而且很容易得罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a hard person to compliment. And an easy one to offend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没那么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里学会开枪的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where'd you learn how to shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈 在后院打锡罐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mom. Tin cans in the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她认为任何独居的女性 都应该知道怎么开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She believed any woman who lived alone should know how to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你呢  -我爸…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You? - My dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎鹿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hunting deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该要工作 而不是去约会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm supposed to be working, not going on dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这是心有旁骛 -坠入爱河不是心有旁骛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a distraction. Falling in love is not a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有坠入爱河\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来五个月会决定我们的下半辈子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, these next five months decide the rest of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何五个月都会决定我们的下半辈子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any five months decide the rest of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些月份就是比较重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, some months are more important than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学时我有朋友都在胡搞瞎搞 现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had friends in high school who...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们有的是时间 但就是无法改变自己的人生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}messed around and now they have all the time in the world, but they can't change their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:17:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那种感觉 那是内疚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know these feelings. It's guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱上某个人时 也会有这种感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt the same way when I'd fall for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有爱上他 我只是…喜欢他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I haven't fallen for him, I just... I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 内疚就是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For me the guilt is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没有结婚 对你来说 就是职业道德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...because I'm not married. For you it's work ethic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈从来没有跟任何人约会过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mom never dated anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸离家出走时 她答应我绝不会带男朋友回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When my dad... walked out, she promised me she'd never bring a boyfriend home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都没有父亲 所以 她要弥补这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never had a father, so she was gonna make up for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是当我年纪渐长…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when I got older, you know, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并意识到这让她付出了什么代价 我应该要说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and realized what this was costing her, I-I should have said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“没关系的 你可以去约会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"It's fine, you can date.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必是孤单一人”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to be alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许如果我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe if I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:18:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 你可以去约会 你不必是孤单孤单一人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's fine. You can date. You don't have to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你可以跟我来吗  -是 长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you come with me, please? Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在训练的这个阶段 我们会再次进行测谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At this point in the training, we repeat your polygraph test
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后比较两次的反应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and compare your responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会只有你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would it only be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法放松 我不想要你因为紧张而没过关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try to relax. I'd hate to fail you because you couldn't relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否服用过任何非法毒品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you ever taken any illegal narcotics?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在申请表里填了你曾吸过几次大麻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You listed on your application the occasions you smoked marijuana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-现在还是只有那几次吗  -是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are these still the only occasions? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在做爱之后抽的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Were they after sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令堂曾经对处方药上瘾吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was your mother ever addicted to prescription medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经对处方药上瘾吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you ever been addicted to prescription medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个过程中 你是否隐瞒了任何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You concealed anything during this process
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会对你的申请 造成负面影响的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which might negatively influence your application?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先前的答案是“否” 你现在要把它改成“是”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your previous answer was no. You're changing your answer to yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你先前说谎吗  -否\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you lie before? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是新发生的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is something new?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个问题 你可以不用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the next question, I'm going to release you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只回答“是”与“否”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the obligation saying yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你隐瞒了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What have you concealed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你重新接受过测谎了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you retaken the polygraph?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个星期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是吗 结果如何  -一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah? How'd it go? The same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么话也不跟我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't say something to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有把我们的事情告诉他们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you tell them about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的事 没有 你有吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About us? No. Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们问我有没有隐瞒任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean... they asked me if I was concealing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是在说我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They weren't talking about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道 这违反规定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you know? This is against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么规定  -联邦调查局学员守则\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What rules? The agent trainee rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你真的读了那种东西  -拜托 这很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You actually read those? Come on. This is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里又不是中学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你觉得 我们不需要让盖布瑞和茱儿知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you don't think we need to let Gabriel and Drew know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:21:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不关他们的事 -每件事都关他们的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's none of their business. Everything is their business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:21:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-介意我跟你一起走吗  -当然不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mind if I walk with you? Oh, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要谈谈你的测谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to talk about your polygraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没通过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, did I fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我现在不是 以指导者的身分讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I'm not speaking as your supervisor right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.17,0:22:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从女性获准加入调查局以来 就一直有绯闻或情侣产生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ever since women were allowed to join, there have been hookups and couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人到后来甚至还结了婚 但多数人没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some even end up getting married. Most don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让你感到尴尬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not trying to embarrass you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想让你察觉我们处境的现实面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just wanted you to be aware of the reality of our situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不顺利 情况变得糟糕的总是女性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it doesn't work out, the woman always comes off worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭受打击的总是女性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She always takes the hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该是这样 但现实就是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It shouldn't be that way. But it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要叫你采取不同的作法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm not telling you to do anything differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:22:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是要告诉你 事情就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm telling you the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初入职场时 我涉入一起事件 变成了被指责的对象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was in an incident at the beginning of my career, for which I was blamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一起探员对探员的枪击事件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was an agent-on-agent shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你开枪打探员  -不是 我是挨子弹的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You shot an agent? - No. I was the one who was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你说被怪罪的人是你  -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said you were blamed? I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.31,0:23:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们提出的原因是说我在错误的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of the reasons they gave was they said I was in the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我在的位置跟男性一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I was in the same place as the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是对方的枪法太差 我早就没命了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, I'd be dead if they weren't such lousy shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你为什么还留在局里  -我不能让他们赢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you stay in the Bureau? I couldn't let 'em win.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.66,0:23:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是当年度最佳学员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was one of the best trainees my year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.66,0:23:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我康复 我就回到了教室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, when I recovered, I just came back to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…这里是唯一 能让我有所成就的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause... that's the only place I was ever allowed to be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.93,0:24:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（未来 2034年）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.71,0:24:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.46,0:24:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.22,0:24:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以进去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.48,0:24:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房子很大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Big house.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.19,0:24:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 有女孩子在的时候 感觉不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, it's nice when the girls stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.86,0:24:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的情况有多频繁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How often is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.40,0:24:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如我想要的那么频繁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not as often as I'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.24,0:25:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.78,0:25:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我也觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.80,0:25:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依靠家庭关系想要了解…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I leaned on my family connections to try and see if...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.17,0:25:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是盟友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you know, who was an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.14,0:25:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lot of people are...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.76,0:25:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很担心这套系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}really worried about this system.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.89,0:25:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们认为它太庞大 也太强大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, they think it's too big, it's too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.85,0:25:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人只会在私底下表达担忧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lot of people will only express their concerns in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.28,0:25:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有太多人愿意帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not a lot are willing to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.65,0:25:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不令人讶异 对吧  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No surprise there, right? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.78,0:25:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是谈论就可能让人惹上麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even talking can get people in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.50,0:25:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人因为我接近他们而感到生气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some got mad at me for approaching them
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.96,0:25:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-面对面 远离摄影机 -你爸有帮助吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}face-to-face, away from cameras. Is your dad helping?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.38,0:25:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他认识人面广的人 其中包括史宾塞参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knows people that know people, including Senator Spenser, 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.09,0:26:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我正在设法安排会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I'm trying to... set up a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.10,0:26:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就像我说的 人们很害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But like I said, people are scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.31,0:26:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是 在这件事…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to say that... you know, before this goes too far,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.78,0:26:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得不可收拾之前 你不必为了我而一起调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you don't have to be a part of the investigation into Tayo's system 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.07,0:26:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-泰约的系统 -诗人 别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for my sake. Poet, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.29,0:26:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你可以自己进行 我懂 -你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can do it on your own. I-I get it. You...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.87,0:26:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是认为我喜欢自己一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You always had it in your mind that I preferred to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.88,0:26:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你一向如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you always are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.34,0:26:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的话也没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If not me, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.59,0:26:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至少要有别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.48,0:26:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.40,0:26:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.19,0:27:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次感觉不错时 你总是不相信 好像那不会是真的一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every time something feels good, you mistrust it. Like it can't be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.20,0:27:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会不断测试 直到它崩坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you test it and you test it until it breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.95,0:27:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你会对自己说 “看吧 我一直都是对的”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you say to yourself, "You see? I was right all along."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.25,0:27:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们之间没有成功的原因吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that why we didn't make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.42,0:27:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我生命中的每件事 看起来都很轻松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe everything in my life seemed too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.47,0:27:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你不想要成为其中一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you wouldn't be another one of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.27,0:27:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我现在可以跟你说…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I can tell you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.60,0:27:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱上你并不轻松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}loving you has not been easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.19,0:27:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我已经爱你二十年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I've loved you for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.70,0:27:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是为什么你不应该牵扯进这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is why you should not be involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.08,0:27:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗人 这次不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not this time, Poet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.96,0:27:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你必须告诉我毫无机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This time, you're gonna have to tell me it doesn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.13,0:28:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不会是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This time, it's not gonna be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.07,0:29:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图皮瑞克能让人渗透进局里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could Tupirik have people infiltrate the Bureau?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.62,0:29:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.20,0:29:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一直都有查核 -测谎吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are checks. The polygraph?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.42,0:29:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我测谎时就说谎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I lied on mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.42,0:29:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对什么事说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What'd you lie about?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.96,0:29:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有真正重要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only the really important things.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.47,0:29:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几个州发起了至少十几次的搜索行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At least a dozen manhunts
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.64,0:29:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要逮捕马克图皮瑞克 民兵组织的其他主要成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for additional key members of Mark Tupirik's militia are underway in multiple states...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.85,0:29:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前调查局正试图厘清\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as the Bureau attempts to figure out the scope
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.90,0:29:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府民兵运动的范围与规模\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and scale of his anti-government militia.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.98,0:29:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪枝射击评鉴就在今天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Firearms assessment is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.42,0:30:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.80,0:30:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.13,0:30:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We go today.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.22,0:30:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你看一下萤幕上的这些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at the people on this screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.57,0:31:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在怕什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.12,0:31:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为自己很容易就会被…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think you'll be too easy to read?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.54,0:31:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样的人看穿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By a man like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.26,0:31:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统发现情绪紧张的动作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The system is picking up elevated movements,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.22,0:31:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳孔放大 心跳加快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}pupil dilation, heart rate increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.35,0:31:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们找到人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.02,0:31:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.99,0:32:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前见过这个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen this man before.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.71,0:32:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在车库里施工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doing construction in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.25,0:32:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为嫌犯可能就在宽提科\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We think the suspect may be at Quantico.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.76,0:32:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听令 一边向前走 一边射击目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the signal, walk forward while shooting at the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.72,0:32:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人开枪…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shooter! Shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.60,0:32:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嘿 -快逃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.62,0:32:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.07,0:33:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她流了好多血 -干得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's losing so much blood. You're gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.99,0:33:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宽提科有警报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's an alert at Quantico.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.58,0:33:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我想请你立刻跟我碰面 -在哪里 这里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. I need you to meet me right now. Where? Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.67,0:33:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我错了 我来承担 但我们必须疏散这栋大楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take the heat if I'm wrong, but we need to evacuate this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.71,0:33:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.18,0:33:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意…请立刻撤离这栋建筑物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Attention, attention. Please evacuate this building immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.69,0:33:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是演习\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is not a drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.69,0:33:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意…请立刻撤离这栋建筑物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Attention. Attention. Please evacuate this building immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.15,0:33:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是演习\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is not a drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.20,0:34:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意…请立刻撤离这栋建筑物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Attention. Attention. Please evacuate this building immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.66,0:34:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是演习\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is not a drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.51,0:34:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.89,0:35:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 换下一根柱子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.81,0:35:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 不要动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.52,0:35:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放轻松…我只是要去找我的主管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy. Easy. I just got to go get my supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.01,0:35:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意…请立刻撤离这栋建筑物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hurry! Please evacuate this building immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.68,0:35:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是演习\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is not a drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.81,0:35:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疏散…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.67,0:36:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须离开 现在就走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to go! We have to go now!
